Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Mix green beans, celery soup, sour cream, shoepeg corn, Cheddar cheese, water chestnuts, and lemon juice together in a bowl; spread into a casserole dish. Mix crackers and butter together in a bowl; sprinkle over the casserole. Bake in preheated oven until hot and bubbly, about 45 minutes.